<p><strong>Saving Throws</strong> Dex +2, Con +4, Wis +2, Cha +2</p>

<p><strong>Skills</strong> Perception +4, Stealth +2</p>

<p><strong>Damage Immunities</strong> cold</p>

<p><strong>Senses</strong> blindsight 10 ft., darkvision 60 ft.</p>

<p><strong>Languages</strong> Draconic</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 2 (450 XP)</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 7 (1d10 + 2) piercing damage plus 2 (1d4) cold damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Cold Breath (Recharge 5-6).</em></strong> The dragon exhales an icy blast of hail in a 15-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC 12 Constitution saving throw, taking 22 (5d8) cold damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>

